CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 23, 1946, pg. 20, reads: "Princess and Singer - Princess Lo Rae, who is currently featured as an exotic, acrobatic dancer in a local night club, is pictured off duty with a friend, Jean Niles, singer.  The princess who is in private life Mrs. Lorraine Tucker, plans a trip to Europe soon. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dancer "Princess Lo Rae" Lorraine Tucker, and singer Jean Niles seated on cabinet in interior with textured glass window
